---
title: Skillet Seitan Enchiladas with Poblano and Monterrey Jack
description: We’ve officially fallen in love with seitan! This Japanese wheat-based protein is paired with boldly spiced enchilada sauce, lending this dish a deliciously smoky flavor. Of course, the best part is the gooey cheese on top!
